<div type="abstract"><head>Peter Kragen an Heinrich Lamprecht, Ritter</head><p>Peter Kragen gewährt Lamprecht und seinem Oheim Eberhard von Thüngfeld sowie deren Gefolge bis Antoniustag Geleit für acht Tage.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_204" id="101v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_204_r2l17"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Lemplein </del> Lampreht <expan>Ritt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_204_r2l18">von Peter Kragen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_204_r2l19">Lıeber her <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> / Als Jr mir <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / 
<del rend="strikethrough">daʒ Jch e </del> von geleits </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_204_r2l20">wegen ew vnd <expan>Eberharte<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>Tün<ex>n</ex>felt</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> öheim / iſt mir 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ewr </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_204_r2l21">derſelb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> brief erſt nehtein <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> worden / vnd alſo han Jch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_204_r2l22">ew als heute mit <expan>meine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vom Rate auſʒgetragen / vvenn das iſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_204_r2l24">daʒ Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_204_r2l23">vnd der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> öheim <expan>Eberh<ex>art</ex></expan> von Tünfelt </ab></add> <expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd ſant Anthoni tag ſchierſt / her
<del rend="strikethrough">ein</del> gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_204_r2l26"> <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> kumpt / daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan></del> Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> öheim <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> von Tunfelt </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_204_r2l25"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_204_r2l27">vnd auch alle die dıe mit ew <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> Acht tag 
<add><ab facs="#facs_204_line_1576594839921_8578">Jr </ab></add> ſıcher geleit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_204_r2l28"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſüllen von Jn vnd cʒu Jn für ſie vnd alle dıe Jren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_204_r2l29"><expan>ongeu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> / da vviſʒt ew nach cʒu <expan>richte<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in vigilia <expan>Circu<ex>m</ex>c<ex>iſionis</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_204_r2l30"><expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nj</expan> Anno xj<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_204" id="101v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Lampreht, <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Von Peter Kragen.<lb/> Lieber her <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir mir
                                <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von geleits wegen ew und
                                <expan>Eberharte<ex>n</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>Tün<ex>n</ex>felt</expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> öheim,
                        ist mir derselb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> brief erst nehtein
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> worden; und also han ich ew als
                        heute mit <expan>meine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vom rate auszgetragen, wenn das ist, daz ir
                            <add>und der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> öheim <expan>Eberh<ex>art</ex></expan> von
                            Tünfelt</add>
<expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <app><note><q type="date">sant Anthoni tag schierst</q>17.01.1411</note></app> her gen
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> kumpt, daz ir
                                    <add><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan></add> und auch alle die, die
                        mit ew <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan>, acht tag <add>ir</add> sicher
                        geleit <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> süllen von in und czu in, für sie und
                        alle die iren <expan>ongeu<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, da wiszt ew nach czu
                                <expan>richte<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in
                        vigilia <expan>circu<ex>m</ex>c<ex>isionis</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>ni</expan> anno xi<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
